# Agent baseline (Cursor)

**Git:** Do not commit, push, merge, or open a pull request unless the user explicitly requests that action. Casual wrap-up language is not permission.

**Portable baseline (full policy and scope):** `docs/agent-guidelines.md`.

**Canonical messaging guardrails** in sibling `.mdc` files apply when editing canonical positioning under `products/`, `framework/`, `use-cases-value-pillars/`, `offerings/`, and `reference/` (see baseline). **Terminology and naming** in `terminology-and-naming.mdc` stays repo-wide unless an edit is purely non-prose automation.
